<item>
            <title>[LU-11382] Graceful Router Reboots</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11382</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In a cluster with more than one router what is the most graceful way to reboot some or all of the routers, without causing client/server connective issues.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="53326">LU-11382</key>
            <summary>Graceful Router Reboots</summary>
